Hi,
I am using Generic Rest API MA for Google MA and able to provision users from FIM to Google.When i do an export on Google, the user provisioned and I am doing a Import on Google again. After that i changed the user at FIM(modify firstName/LastName), and did a delta Import and delta Sync on FIM MA. On doing Delta Sync,the update is not relecting and giving an error "object already exists in Google MA".

If I do a change without doing a Import on Google MA, then update is working fine without any errors.

Can you pleas suggest, why the error is generating with Import on Google MA(Import done After doing an Export on Google MA).

Hi,

This MA does not support delta import/sync, so please use full import / synchronization.

Thanks
